r [[Record Store Day]], [[Glass Records]] reissued the album on 12\" Duck Egg coloured vinyl<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.roughtrade.com/gb/prolapse/backsaturday|title=backsaturday \u2013 Prolapse - RSD 2019 &#124; Rough Trade Records |work=roughtrade.com}}</ref>. \n\n==Track listing==\nAll songs written by Prolapse\n\n{{Tracklist\n| headline        = Side 1\n| title1          = Flex\n| length1         = 15:07\n| total_length    = 15:07\n}}\n{{Tracklist\n| headline        = Side 2\n| title1          = Mein Minefield, Mine Landmine\n| length1         = 2:19\n| title2          = Framen Fr. Cesar\n| length2         = 7:53\n| title3          = Every Night I'm Mentally Crucified (7000 Times)\n| length3         = 2:19\n| title4          = Zen Nun Deb\n| length4         = 5:52\n| title5          = Drown Radio Therapy\n| length5         = 1:40\n| title6          = Strain Contortion Of Bag\n| length6         = 2:23\n| total_length    = 22:26\n}}\n\n{{Tracklist\n| headline        = US CD Release\n| title1          = Mein Minefield, Mine Landmine\n| length1         = 2:21\n| title2          = T.C.R.\n| length2         = 3:16\n| title3          = Framen Fr. Cesar\n| length3         = 7:53\n| title4          = Every Night I'm Mentally Crucified (7000 Times)\n| length4         = 2:20\n| title5          = Zen Nun Deb\n| length5         = 5:54\n| title6          = Irritating Radiator\n| length6         = 5:36\n| title7          = Drown Radio Therapy\n| length7         = 1:38\n| title8          = Flex\n| length8         = 15:04\n| title9          = Strain Contortion Of Bag\n| length9         = 2:24\n| total_length    = 46:26\n}}\n\n==Personnel==\n===Band===\n* Mick Derrick - vocals, stylophone\n* Mick Harrison - bass, guitar\n* David Jeffreys - guitar, vocals\n* Pat Marsden - guitar, keyboards\n* Tim Pattinson - drums\n* Linda Steelyard - vocals, keyboard, recorder\n===Additional===\n* Jonathan Barrett - guest vocal on ''Zen Nun Deb''\n===Production===\n* Produced and engineered b