iation |date= 28 Dec 2017}}</ref> through [[Sberbank of Russia]]}}\n|-\n|27 Aug 2013\n|{{flagicon|Russia}} [[Utair]]\n|<abbr title=\"To be announced\">TBA</abbr>\n|\u2014\n|10\n|\u2014\n|10{{efn|through [[Vnesheconombank|VEB Leasing]]}}\n|-\n|29 Aug 2013\n|{{flagicon|Russia}} [[Sberbank|Sberbank Leasing]]\n|2019\n|\u2014\n|20\n|\u2014\n|20<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.flightglobal.com/news/articles/maks-sberbank-signs-for-20-mc-21s-and-20-superjets-389976/|title=MAKS: Sberbank signs for 20 MC-21s and 20 Superjets|date=29 August 2013|website=flightglobal.com}}</ref>\n|-\n|30 Aug 2013\n|{{flagicon|Russia}} [[Red Wings Airlines]]\n|2019\n|\u2014\n|16\n|\u2014\n|16<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.flightglobal.com/news/articles/maks-red-wings-signs-for-russian-jets-and-q400s-390028/|title=MAKS: Red Wings signs for Russian jets and Q400s|date=30 Aug 2013|work=Flight Global}}</ref>{{efn|name=Ilyushin|through [[Ilyushin]] Finance}}\n|-\n|9 Sep 2015\n|{{flagicon|Egypt}} [[Cairo Aviation]]\n|<abbr title=\"To be announced\">TBA</abbr>\n|\u2014\n|6\n|4\n|10<ref>{{cite news|url=https://af.reuters.com/article/commoditiesNews/idAFL8N1343HC20151109/|title=Russia's Irkut to sell six MC-21 airliners to Egypt's Cairo Aviation|date=9 November 2015|work=Thomson Reuters Africa}}</ref>\n|-\n|8 Jun 2016\n|{{flagicon|Azerbaijan}} [[Azerbaijan Airlines]]\n|2019\n|\u2014\n|10\n|\u2014\n|10<ref name=\"Flight13Jun2016\" />\n|-\n|18 Jul 2017\n|{{flagicon|Russia}} [[VIM Airlines]]\n|2021\n|\u2014\n|15\n|\u2014\n|15<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://atwonline.com/aircraft-orders-deliveries/irkut-mc-21-gets-new-orders-maks-air-show|title=Irkut MC-21 gets new orders at MAKS Air Show|date=18 July 2017|website=atwonline.com|language=en-GB|access-date=19 July 2017}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.ch-aviation.com/portal/news/57941-russias-vim-airlines-to-lease-15-mc-21s-from-ifc|title=Russia's VIM Airlines to lease 15 MC-21s from IFC|date=19 July 2017|website=atwonline.com|language=en-GB|access-date=19 