 | position=CB | collegeyear=2016 | college=Michigan | collegeteam=Michigan Wolverines | collegelink=Michigan | probowl= |note= |cfb page exists= yes}}\n\n{{NFLDraft-row |draftyear= 2017 |round=3 | picknum=95 | team=Seattle Seahawks | first=Lano | last=Hill |dab= | position=S | collegeyear=2016 | college=Michigan | collegeteam=Michigan Wolverines | collegelink=Michigan | probowl= |note=from [[2017 Atlanta Falcons season|Atlanta]]&nbsp;{{#tag:ref|{{Anchor|McKinleyTrade}}'''No. 95: Atlanta \u2192 Seattle (D).''' [[2017 Seattle Seahawks season|Seattle]] traded their first-round selection ([[#Pick 26|26th]]) to [[2017 Atlanta Falcons season|Atlanta]] in exchange for Atlanta's first-, third-, and seventh-round selections ([[#Pick 31|31st]], [[#Pick 95|95th]], and [[#Pick 249|249th]]).<ref name=\"2017TradeTracker\"/>}} |cfb page exists=yes }}\n\n{{NFLDraft-row |draftyear= 2017 |compensatory=yes |round=3 | picknum=106 | team=Seattle Seahawks | first=Amara | last=Darboh |dab= | position=WR | collegeyear=2016 | college=Michigan | collegeteam=Michigan Wolverines | collegelink=Michigan | probowl= |note= |cfb page exists= yes}}\n\n{{NFLDraft-row |draftyear= 2017 |round=4 | picknum=120 | team=Minnesota Vikings | first=Ben | last=Gedeon |dab= | position=LB | collegeyear=2016 | college=Michigan | collegeteam=Michigan Wolverines | collegelink=Michigan | probowl= |note= |cfb page exists=yes }}\n\n{{NFLDraft-row |draftyear= 2017 |compensatory=yes |round=4 | picknum=138 | team=Cincinnati Bengals | first=Ryan | last=Glasgow |dab= | position=DT | collegeyear=2016 | college=Michigan | collegeteam=Michigan Wolverines | collegelink=Michigan | probowl= |note= |cfb page exists=yes }}\n\n{{NFLDraft-row |draftyear= 2017 |compensatory=yes |round=4 | picknum=139 | team=Kansas City Chiefs | first=Jehu | last=Chesson |dab= | position=WR | collegeyear=2016 | college=Michigan | collegeteam=Michigan Wolverines | collegelink=Michigan | probowl= |note=from [[2017 Cleveland Browns season|Cleveland]] via