 this year's selections came in the first four rounds, setting another program record. It was also the most draftees in the 2017 NFL Draft by any school.<ref>{{cite news|title=U-M Leads All Programs in Players Picked in 2017 NFL Draft|publisher=CBS Interactive|work=MGoBlue.com|accessdate=April 29, 2017|date=April 29, 2017|url=http://www.mgoblue.com/sports/m-footbl/spec-rel/042917abg.html}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Michigan Sets Record on Day Three of NFL Draft|publisher=CBS Interactive|work=MGoBlue.com|accessdate=April 29, 2017|date=April 29, 2017|url=http://www.mgoblue.com/sports/m-footbl/spec-rel/042917aag.html}}</ref>\n\n==Roster==\n{{American football roster/Header|year=2016|team=Michigan Wolverines|teamcolors=y\n|offensive_players=\n{{American football roster/Player|first=Kekoa|last=Crawford|num=1|pos=WR|class=F}}\n{{American football roster/Player|first=Devin|last=Asiasi|num=2|pos=TE|class=F|link=y}}\n{{American football roster/Player|first=Wilton|last=Speight|num=3|pos=QB|class=J|link=y}}\n{{American football roster/Player|first=De'Veon|last=Smith|num=4|pos=RB|class=S|link=y}}\n{{American football roster/Player|first=Michael|last=Sessa|num=6|pos=QB|class=F}}\n{{American football roster/Player|first=Kareem|last=Walker|num=6|pos=RB|class=F|link=y}}\n{{American football roster/Player|first=Shane|last=Morris|num=7|pos=QB|class=S|link=y}}\n{{American football roster/Player|first=John|last=O'Korn|num=8|pos=QB|class=S|link=y}}\n{{American football roster/Player|first=Grant|last=Perry|num=9|pos=WR|class=SO}}\n{{American football roster/Player|first=Alex|last=Malzone|num=10|pos=QB|class=SO}}\n{{American football roster/Player|first=Chris|last=Evans|dab=Chris Evans (American football)|num=12|pos=RB|class=F|link=y}}\n{{American football roster/Player|first=Eddie|last=McDoom|num=13|pos=WR|class=F}}\n{{American football roster/Player|first=Drake|last=Harris|num=14|pos=WR|class=J}}\n{{American football roster/Player|first=Garrett|last=Moores|num=15|pos=QB|class=S}}\n{{A